text: Vadim Nikolaevich Krasnoselsky (; ; born 14 April 1970) is a Transnistrian politician who is the 3rd and current President of Transnistria since 2016. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Transnistria Category:Current national leaders Category:People from Zabaykalsky Krai Vadim Krasnoselsky's office is in the city of Tiraspol. He has two children namely Sofia Krasnoselskaya and Ivan Kranoselskaya respectively
title: Vadim Krasnoselsky
